l for=20
demolishing 17 Palestinian houses in Rafah refugee camp in the Gaza strip.=
=20
Earlier, Israel had destroyed 14 houses under construction in a refugee cam=
p=20
in Jerusalem.
=09=09=09=09
=09=09=09=09See article: Post-mortem on Black October=20
=09=09=09=09
=09=09=09=09Israel, Hizbullah and the United Nations were involved in a row=
 over a=20
videotape taken at the scene of the abduction of three Israeli soldiers las=
t=20
year. The UN is prepared to show Israel the footage, but only on the=20
condition that the faces of Hizbullah militants are obscured.=20
=09=09=09=09
=09=09=09=09A leading Egyptian feminist, Nawal el-Saadawi, was accused of a=
postasy by a=20
lawyer for allegedly saying the haj pilgrimage had pagan roots. A Cairo cou=
rt=20
is being asked to enforce her separation from her Muslim husband of 37 year=
s.=20
The case has been adjourned.=20
